close_reason: "Shipped `pm package init --declarative`: scaffolds a composeExtension blueprint starter (defineExtensionBlueprint → composeExtension) with an author-time assertExtensionPreflight + createExtensionTestHarness test. Package-mode + commands only (composeExtension is a runtime SDK value import), with clear USAGE errors for extension-mode, non-commands capabilities, and non-init use. Wired through register-setup/extension/completion/cli-contracts (+regenerated contracts snapshot) and documented in SDK.md. 5049 tests, 100/100/100/100 coverage, all quality gates green; manually dogfooded end-to-end (scaffold → typecheck → node --test → install → dispatch). Full-capability-matrix generalization tracked in pm-lfdv."
body: "## Implementation (2026-06-24)\n\n`pm package init <path> --declarative` scaffolds the SDK's declarative authoring loop.\n\n**Generated files (declarative, package-mode + commands):**\n- `index.ts`: `defineCommand` → `defineExtensionBlueprint({ commands, deactivate })` → `export default composeExtension(blueprint)` (exports `pingCommand`/`blueprint`/default module).\n- `index.test.ts`: author-time `assertExtensionPreflight(blueprint, { identity, target })` (asserts derived + synthesized `capabilities: [\"commands\"]`) + runtime `createExtensionTestHarness(extension)` (`assertCommandContract`/`runCommand`/`deactivate`).\n- `README.md`: \"## Declarative Authoring\" section; package.json/manifest.json/tsconfig.json/.gitignore byte-identical to the imperative commands starter.\n\n**Constraints (enforced in `scaffoldExtensionProject`, USAGE exit):**\n- package-mode only — `composeExtension` is a runtime SDK value import (extension-only installs stay import-free per SDK.md).\n- commands capability only (canonical example); follow-up [[pm-lfdv]] generalizes to all 9 capabilities.\n- `--declarative` only valid with `--init/--scaffold`.\n\n**Wiring:** `register-setup.ts` (commander option on both lifecycle + init sub-command, options reader), `extension.ts` (option type, validation, passthrough, `style` in result), `completion.ts` (bash/zsh/fish), `cli-contracts.ts` (`EXTENSION_FLAG_CONTRACTS` + `EXTENSION_INIT_FLAG_CONTRACTS`) + regenerated `tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json`.\n\n**Verification:** 5049 tests, 100/100/100/100 coverage; typecheck (src+packages+examples), static-quality (100% docstrings), docs-skills gates green. Manual dogfood in a temp workspace: scaffold → `tsc --noEmit` clean → `node --test` 2/2 pass → `pm install --project` → `pm <cmd> ping` dispatches the composed module (SDK linked). All three error paths return exit 2 with clear messages."
